Winter is coming !

Challenge your friends and players from all around the world in this highly tactical multiplayer turn-based strategy game ! Hire the right troops at the right time, conquer the map to earn more gold and get more bonuses, surround your enemies and victory is yours !

Resource management, lands' conquests, random maps, consideration of units' morale and experience, armies' resupplying : Warlords gathers all the classical elements of strategy games (Warcraft, Dawn of War, Heroes of Might and Magic...), and board games (A Game of Thrones, Warhammer, 40k...).

*** AWESOME FEATURES ***
- up to 8 players on the same map !
- 5 different armies for different gaming experiences !
- evil AI in solo and multiplayer modes
- chat in multiplayer games
- best generals ranking !
- fully integrated with Google Game Services (ranking, achievements, ...)

This game has been developed for strategy games fans on my spare time. Do not hesitate to contact me about any issue/feedback/cool idea you may have !